              "lines": [
                "## Databricks Release Notes Tracker\n",
                "AWS & Azure release notes, upcoming features, and breaking changes — updated daily.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Impact classification:** **High** = breaking changes, deprecations, behavior changes · **Medium** = GA releases, upcoming features, general updates · **Low** = Public Preview, Beta, Maintenance"
              ]
